snippet.title: SpongeBob Squarepants ™: The Patrick Star Game – Announcement Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
SpongeBob SquarePants: The Patrick Star Game launches October 4, 2024 on Nintendo Switch! Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/spongebob-squarepants-the-patrick-star-game-switch/?utm_source=SW&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=P1057-01&utm_id=P1057-01

Explore Bikini Bottom as a sandbox playground, using various objects to create physics-defying fun. The game features missions from beloved characters like SpongeBob, Mr. Krabs, Sandy, and Plankton, and includes iconic locations such as Glove World, The Dump, and Demolition Derby. Activities range from building Krabby Patties to causing chaos in Mrs. Puff’s rage room!

#ThePatrickStarGame #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/
